    "The results show that the model pretrained on English data, namely, SciBERT outperformed the other models trained on German language data (in terms of f1 and recall score for both exact and partial matches).",
    "BioGottBert performed best in precision.",
    "Further, it can be observed that we obtained a higher precision score, especially when the data were validated using entitytype validation, with a precision of 0.85 for SCAI-BIO/ bio-gottbert.",
